%F A167374 T = A130595*A156644 = M*T^(-1)*M = M*A000012*M, where M(n,k) = (-1)^n A130595(n,k). Note that M = M^(-1). Cf. A118800 and A097805. - _Tom Copeland_, Nov 15 2016
